title: Arturo Sandoval - How To Be Happy
fulltitle: Arturo Sandoval - How To Be Happy

description:
Jazz legend Arturo Sandoval discusses what he feels is most important in life: being happy. According to Sandoval, “if you are in love with music, I promise you you’re gonna be a happy person.” He also discusses how a serious musician must live the passion by practicing and perfecting their craft every day.
